    "content": "<p>Consider the following three structures :&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Structure I :</span>&nbsp;Beam with hinge support at A, roller at C, guided roller at E, and internal hinges at B and D</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3s37/0f6e046e-0bec-4bc1-9e78-72b444e48bac/63ed7430-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3s38.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3s37/0f6e046e-0bec-4bc1-9e78-72b444e48bac/63ed7430-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3s38.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English 1\">\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Structure II :</span>&nbsp;Pin-jointed truss, with hinge support at A, and rollers at B and D</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3m31/45ace60d-04bb-4700-aec8-a6dc16ef3eba/5f4a03d0-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3m32.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3m31/45ace60d-04bb-4700-aec8-a6dc16ef3eba/5f4a03d0-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3m32.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English 2\">\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Structure III :</span>&nbsp;Pin-jointed truss, with hinge support at A and roller at C</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3h8c/ea632a1f-bbee-4177-bcd3-3d74fa8a204d/5b8a3cb0-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3h8d.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfm3h8c/ea632a1f-bbee-4177-bcd3-3d74fa8a204d/5b8a3cb0-5267-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfm3h8d.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English 3\">\n<p>Which of the following statements is/are TRUE?</p>\n",
