    "explanation": "<p>I.</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfmaj7x/c1640474-11d1-46e3-aafa-0f1791ebbd86/1fbd97d0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaj7y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfmaj7x/c1640474-11d1-46e3-aafa-0f1791ebbd86/1fbd97d0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaj7y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English Explanation 1\">\n\n<p>$$ D_s=r-s=3-4=-1 $$</p>\n\n<p>$D_s$ is negative so Structure is unstable</p>\n\n<p>II.</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfmagjx/d3ccfcb1-94d7-4d7a-b16d-7532fdf5403c/1db5e0f0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaglb.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfmagjx/d3ccfcb1-94d7-4d7a-b16d-7532fdf5403c/1db5e0f0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaglb.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English Explanation 2\">\n\n<p>III.</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lzfmadda/a9370c3a-9d60-4f79-8e10-6b8c7b9ddd35/1b3884e0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaddb.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lzfmadda/a9370c3a-9d60-4f79-8e10-6b8c7b9ddd35/1b3884e0-5268-11ef-97a1-3b03a4a4f826/file-jaoe38c1lzfmaddb.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2023 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Stability and Static Indeterminacy Question 1 English Explanation 3\">\n\n<p>Hence, the correct options are (A), (B) and (C).</p>",
